# Impeccable Style

## Typography
- Import distinctive Google Fonts. Never default to Inter, Roboto, Arial, or system fonts.
- Pair a characterful display font with a refined body font.
- Use a modular type scale with fluid sizing (`clamp()`).

## Color
- Use CSS custom properties for a cohesive palette. Tint neutrals toward the brand hue.
- No pure black (#000) or pure white (#fff). Avoid the "AI palette" (cyan-on-dark, purple gradients, neon glow).
- Use `oklch` or `color-mix` for perceptually uniform tones when practical.

## Layout
- Embrace asymmetry, varied spacing, and intentional grid-breaking for emphasis.
- Not everything needs a card. Avoid card-in-card nesting.
- Use container queries (`@container`) for component-level responsiveness.

## Motion
- Staggered entrance reveals on page load; smooth ease-out transitions.
- Animate only `transform` and `opacity`. Respect `prefers-reduced-motion`.

## UX
- Progressive disclosure: start simple, reveal depth through interaction.
- Design meaningful empty states. Make every interactive surface responsive.
- Mobile layouts adapt the interface, not amputate it.

## Quality Gate
If someone would immediately say "AI made this," redesign. The goal is work that prompts "how was this made?"
